Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:56.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(538,370)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.98,0:01:03.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每每清晨空气香甜的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:03.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always make lots of money
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.88,0:01:06.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我常常都会赚到大钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:06.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when the morning air smells this good
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.03,0:01:16.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.03,0:01:16.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in Finnegan's Footlocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:16.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(860,536)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.75,0:01:23.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板好像要搬走了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:23.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like Plankton is moving away, Mr. K
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.65,0:01:24.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:24.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.82,0:01:27.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,估计有什么阴谋诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.82,0:01:27.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's planning something
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.15,0:01:28.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个嘛  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:28.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Eugene--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.60,0:01:30.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要永远搬走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:30.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving for good
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.32,0:01:34.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟凯伦要在统治世界之前环游世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen and I are gonna
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:34.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,travel the world before I take it over
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.35,0:01:38.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.35,0:01:38.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.45,0:01:40.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:40.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, okay
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.03,0:01:41.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:41.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, then
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.57,0:01:43.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有缘再见  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.57,0:01:43.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.85,0:01:52.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然你还在  但是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:52.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're still here, but I--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.60,0:01:54.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经在想念你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.60,0:01:54.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I already miss you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.51,0:01:55.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  给我得了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:55.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, that's enough
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.75,0:01:56.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:01:56.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.09,0:02:04.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永别了  蟹黄堡的秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:04.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Krabby Patty secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永别了  裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.87,0:02:10.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:10.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.34,0:02:33.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:33.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm free
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.52,0:02:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.60,0:02:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm free
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.60,0:02:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm free
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没痞老板  我自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more Plankton, me free
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.50,0:02:43.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自由  自由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:43.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free, free
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.89,0:02:46.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也没有痞老板了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:46.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more Plankton, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.43,0:02:48.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:48.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.89,0:02:50.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:50.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, boy-o?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(936,370)}花盆花店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:10.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1280,732)}全新开张\N价格实惠
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,花盆花店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,FlowerPot Florist?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.02,0:03:16.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可爱死价格实惠的插花了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:16.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just love floral arrangements at affordable prices
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就去跟店主套套近乎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd better make friends with the owner right away
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.85,0:03:21.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对不能再跟人家结梁子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:21.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want another crazy feud with him too
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.72,0:03:23.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:23.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.43,0:03:31.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临花盆花店  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:31.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the FlowerPot, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.07,0:03:33.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是店主  佩图尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:33.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the owner, Petunia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:33.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1126,920)}矮  牵  牛
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm Mr--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.60,0:03:36.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必向我自报姓名了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:36.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell me who you are
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是蟹老板  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're Mr. Krab, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你开蟹堡王的  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you run the Krusty Krab, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最爱的餐厅就这家  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my favorite restaurant, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.86,0:03:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你  佩图尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, nice to meet you, Petunia
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是想顺道过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to stop by
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.60,0:03:49.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎你来到这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:49.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and welcome you to the neighborhood
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.57,0:03:52.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随时都可以顺道过来  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:52.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You stop by any time, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, thank ye
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她还真是好心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a nice lady
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.39,0:04:04.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:04.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs is actually buying it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.61,0:04:11.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,使出鲜花美人计
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:11.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This friendly florist farce
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.74,0:04:15.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,定能偷到蟹黄堡的秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:15.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will finally get that Krabby Patty secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  新邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, new neighbor
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.36,0:04:27.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你家的花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:27.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like your flowers
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.72,0:04:30.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时候就应该歇下脚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:30.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you just gotta stop
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.67,0:04:34.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闻闻金鱼草  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:34.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and smell the snapdragons, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要买这朵大的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanna buy this big one
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.20,0:04:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那朵是非卖品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That one's not for sale
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.40,0:04:48.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过这朵可以免费送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:48.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you can have this one for free
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.17,0:05:01.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:01.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get back to your grill
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.62,0:05:04.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我连鼻子都能喷出点餐单了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:04.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got orders coming out of my nose
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.75,0:05:08.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:08.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.63,0:05:10.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:10.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And bye-bye, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.20,0:05:15.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真对不起  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:15.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, miss
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.81,0:05:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝净让人头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob can be a real pain in the--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,佩图尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Petunia
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.75,0:05:25.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:25.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enchanté
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.57,0:05:27.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在下章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:27.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Je suis Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.05,0:05:31.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果需要帮忙摆花的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:31.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you ever need any help arranging your flowers
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就告诉我一声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,give me a holler
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.77,0:05:37.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我当作你的朱兰老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:37.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think of me as your "Pogonia Pappy"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.75,0:05:42.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向朱兰老爸送朵康乃馨  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:39.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's a complimentary carnation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:42.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for "Pogonia Pappy," huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.72,0:05:48.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别看我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:48.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look away
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.19,0:05:50.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我丑死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:50.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hideous
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.68,0:05:57.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这套伪装好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:57.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This disguise is dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}几束花之后
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.57,0:06:02.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽情欣赏黄水仙  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:02.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the daffodils, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.52,0:06:07.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全没人怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:07.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one suspects a thing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好启动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So are you ready
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.66,0:06:13.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鲜花美人计第二阶段了吗  佩图尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:13.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for Faux Florist phase two, Petunia?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.50,0:06:15.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就好  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:15.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soon, my dear
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All in good time
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.92,0:06:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过插花不是很棒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But isn't this arrangement fabulous?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送花时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to make a delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鲜花力量大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Power to the flower
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.03,0:06:39.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:39.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别抠鼻子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't pick your nose
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.72,0:06:53.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挑朵花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:53.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pick a flower
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也太可爱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't this lovely?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.47,0:07:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye now
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.32,0:07:05.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鲜花力量大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:05.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Power to the flower
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.60,0:07:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,贵安  佩图尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bonjour, Petunia
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.00,0:07:11.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想买一束花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:11.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would like to buy a bouquet
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又回来了  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back again, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,建议你少买点  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'd better cut back, Mr. Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.99,0:07:17.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今天已经买四束花了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:17.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is your fourth bouquet today
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, uh--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.59,0:07:22.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:22.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.35,0:07:25.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:25.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.76,0:07:29.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:29.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你省了我不少走过去的工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll save me a trip
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.90,0:07:35.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的蟹堡王花束准备好了  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:35.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your Krusty Krab bouquets are ready, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.27,0:07:38.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:38.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.67,0:07:40.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把袋子抬走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:40.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Carry that bag
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.90,0:07:47.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来抬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:47.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  佩图尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Petunia
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会儿再过来闻花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smell you later
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了  谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did it, Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.50,0:08:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的花马上就会挂满蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab will be festooned with our flowers
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.97,0:08:07.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很快秘方就能到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:07.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soon we will have their formula
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.42,0:08:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know about that
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.96,0:08:14.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实我在考虑把计划搁置一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:12.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was thinking of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:14.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,putting my plan on hold for a while
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.52,0:08:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.32,0:08:18.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当个全职花店店主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:18.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And becoming a full-time florist
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱让客人满面笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love making customers smile
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.75,0:08:23.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉自己真的掌握了插花的诀窍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:21.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I really think
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have the knack for flower arranging
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.28,0:08:27.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:27.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's so sweet
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.72,0:08:31.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的小可爱想当花店店长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:31.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My widdle man wants to be a fworist
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.43,0:08:33.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我的新梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:33.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my new dream
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽情享受你的梦想吧  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy that dream while you can, honey
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.97,0:08:38.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还剩大概五分钟时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:38.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got about five minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.12,0:08:39.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:39.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,计划你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember your plan?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把炸弹花卖给蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sell exploding flowers to Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wait for the timers to go off
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.99,0:08:47.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人全都惊慌失措
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:47.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and while everyone is freaking out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.91,0:08:50.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就径直走进去  取走秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:50.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you walk right in and take the formula
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.25,0:08:56.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王的鼻毛啊  我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:56.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neptune's nose hairs, I forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.10,0:08:58.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须去阻止开花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:58.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've gotta stop those flowers from blooming
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.60,0:09:00.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保住我的新事业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:00.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and save my new career
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.82,0:09:01.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:01.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,佩图尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Petunia
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.16,0:09:10.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你家美丽无比的花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:10.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look how your beautiful flowers
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为蟹堡王增色不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have brightened up the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.99,0:09:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常好  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's great, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.52,0:09:16.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:16.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.40,0:09:25.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:25.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget this
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先把这些花弄新鲜点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just freshen these florets
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.21,0:09:30.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再带回来吧  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:30.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and bring them right back, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.10,0:09:34.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道佩图尼亚怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:34.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's wrong with Petunia
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她才没怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing's wrong with her
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.70,0:09:39.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她跟我一样是完美主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:39.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's a perfectionist like me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.15,0:09:41.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我深深爱上了她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:41.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with her
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个秘密我彻底公开了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I can't keep it a secret any longer
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.15,0:09:48.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,佩图尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:48.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Petunia
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.32,0:09:53.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拆引信的时间只剩一分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:53.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got exactly one minute to defuse these bombs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.87,0:10:00.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从我自家的花园摘的秋海棠  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:10:00.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I picked this begonia from my own flower garden, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常好看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a nice one
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.02,0:10:05.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我现在不能收下  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:05.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I can't right now, Mr. Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你让一让
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please step aside
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,花店店长佩图尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Petunia the florist
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是否能嫁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will you marry--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.12,0:10:20.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这个恋爱脑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:20.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You loopy lovesick lummox
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我计划全搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sabotaged my whole plan
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.98,0:10:38.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不仅仅玩弄了章鱼哥的心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:38.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not only did you play with Squidward's heart
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.40,0:10:42.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还害我损失了24束花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:42.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you cost me 24 bouquets
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.42,0:10:44.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家过来踩他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:44.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say we step on him
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.85,0:10:48.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完蛋了  哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:48.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoopsie daisy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:48.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(858,920)}雏 菊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,佩图尼亚她鱼很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Petunia was very nice
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.97,0:10:57.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我很高兴你回来了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:57.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm so glad you're back, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.65,0:10:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  海绵笨笨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, SpongeBoob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.22,0:11:02.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你送了我最好的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:02.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've given me the greatest gift I could ever ask for
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.95,0:11:05.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮我腾出时间做这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:05.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just enough time to do this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:09.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(978,720)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了  小毛茛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, buttercup
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.52,0:11:14.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:14.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toodle-oo
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不卖花了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more flowers
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要继续偷秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's back to the secret formula for me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的虹膜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My iris
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1024,920)}鸢 尾
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.15,0:11:31.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:31.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.13,0:11:36.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我回来了  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:36.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm back, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:40.97,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFAF&\fs150\fsp45\bord4\shad6}海绵宝宝去游行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:46.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(704,368)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(718,664)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(634,468)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(776,662)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(746,532)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(582,538)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:51.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310,374)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手  不准把你手上的传单
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Avast, keep your proposal and propaganda mitts
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,贴到我门上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,away from me door
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你搞什么啊  我干个活而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, man, I'm just doing my job
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎大家前来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Come one, come all
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.50,0:12:12.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,参加明天举行的裤头村大游行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:12.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the Big Bikini Bottom Parade tomorrow"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.50,0:12:13.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:13.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.92,0:12:17.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,游行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:17.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Parade?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我参军那会儿可没少齐步走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did enough marching when I was in the navy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是游行可以方方便便地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But a parade is a great way
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给蟹堡王免费打广
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get free advertising for the Krusty--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最爱这么组词了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's me favorite assemblage of letters
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.81,0:12:29.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:29.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须要造一辆花车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna have to build a float
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又浪费了一天的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that was another day wasted
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.73,0:12:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今天还没过完呢  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your day's not over, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你和海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you and SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.36,0:12:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,造出来一辆蟹堡王花车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to build a Krusty Krab float
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备明天的裤头村游行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the Bikini Bottom Parade tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个只有十小时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two have ten hours
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.29,0:12:51.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你会搞艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:51.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And since you're the artistic type
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就让你来设计
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you get to design it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,设计
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Design?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.08,0:12:55.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:55.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.17,0:12:58.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  预算有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:58.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, what's the budget?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就属这个我最满意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the best part
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.50,0:13:01.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,预算是零
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:01.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Zero budget
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.96,0:13:05.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要发挥创意  使出想象力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:05.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You get to be creative and use your imagerination
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.55,0:13:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Imagination
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等不及要看你的旷世巨作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't wait to see your masterpiece
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个玩得开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have fun, you two
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.65,0:13:19.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在画什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:19.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatcha drawing?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.48,0:13:20.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:20.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lemme see
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.19,0:13:20.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:20.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanna see
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.86,0:13:21.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:21.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanna see
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.57,0:13:22.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:22.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanna see
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.53,0:13:23.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:23.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, show me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I see?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.11,0:13:24.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:24.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I see?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.86,0:13:25.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:25.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanna see
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go ahead
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我说说你的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me how much you like it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放开了说  我都能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I can take it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先  设计得特别好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First of all, it's genius
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过还需要一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it could use a little--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,造就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just build it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.05,0:13:47.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:47.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.93,0:13:51.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  要上哪找造花车的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:51.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, where do I find building materials?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't care
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪都行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.94,0:13:59.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:13:59.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不管  哪都行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"I don't care, anywhere"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.49,0:14:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  哪都行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, anywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}十小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(438,382)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你睡着的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, you look like a little baby octopus
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真像一只章鱼宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you're asleep
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在几点了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.51,0:14:27.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到游行的点了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:27.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost parade time
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.88,0:14:28.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:28.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I finished it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.47,0:14:32.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为你献上蟹堡王游行花车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:32.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I give you the Krusty Krab parade float
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:33.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(864,370)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把花车做得更切合主题了点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made it a little more on theme
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.93,0:14:38.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,傻蛋主题还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:38.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's moron-themed, all right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:38.39,注释,,0,0,0,,[ moron（傻蛋）与 more on（更切合）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.39,0:14:40.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然连我的画都没用上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:40.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You didn't even use my drawing
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.52,0:14:42.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我用上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:42.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, I did
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.02,0:14:44.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我用那幅画来补蟹黄堡上面的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:44.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I used it to patch up that hole in the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.19,0:14:48.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:48.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,样子看着还行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks fine, I guess
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.45,0:14:53.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方瓶的样子跟真货似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The secret formula bottle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,almost looks like the real thing
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是真货  只不过大点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is, just bigger
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.87,0:14:59.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还把秘方写进里面的纸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I even wrote down the secret formula
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the paper inside
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有咱俩知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only we know
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(972,764)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.38,0:15:05.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还把秘方写进里面的纸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:04.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I even wrote down the secret formula
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:05.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the paper inside
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.38,0:15:08.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有咱俩知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:08.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only we know
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然把秘方写进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wrote down the secret formula?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.93,0:15:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是白痴得恰到好处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That beautiful idiot
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.93,0:15:18.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我要去参加游行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:18.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm going to a parade
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.39,0:15:23.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到裤头村年度大游行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:23.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the annual Bikini Bottom Parade
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.31,0:15:25.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天正是海底举办游行的美好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:25.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it's a beautiful ocean day for it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是帕奇帕金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Perch Perkins
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在市中心为您现场直播
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,coming to you live from downtown
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.45,0:15:33.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在我身边的是今年的联合主持人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:33.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And with me is this year's co-host
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.07,0:15:35.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,举世无双的冰淇淋大王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:35.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the one and only Ice Cream King
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:48.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,242)}裤头村游行
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,您能来是我的荣幸  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to have you, Your Majesty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该叫你大王  还是小冰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do I call you King or Ice?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're that guy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.08,0:15:45.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是怎么从我电视跑出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:45.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How'd you get out of my TV
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.17,0:15:47.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你个坏小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:47.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you bad little boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.59,0:15:48.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还化了妆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:48.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're wearing makeup
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.72,0:15:51.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是小丑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:51.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you a clown?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要气球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want a balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.43,0:15:52.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:52.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.89,0:15:53.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:53.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.22,0:15:54.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会给你气球的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:54.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll get you a balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.64,0:15:58.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今年游行开场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:58.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And to kick off this year's parade
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.06,0:16:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,迎面走来的是裤头村中学巡游乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here comes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Bikini Bottom High School marching band
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.73,0:16:04.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算他们不奏乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:04.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, even when they're not playing
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.65,0:16:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也喜欢凑一块游行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they love to march together
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个乐队实际上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The band is actually
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.23,0:16:11.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由35个相互独立的乐队组成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:11.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,made up of 35 individual bands
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.15,0:16:15.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些年轻人站位十分精准
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:15.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing precision from these youngsters
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.16,0:16:18.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们全都撞衫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:18.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They all wore the same outfit
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.45,0:16:19.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太尴尬了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:19.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How embarrassing
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.08,0:16:23.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美的水母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:23.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A perfect jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那居然是水母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a jellyfish?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一撮头发还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was gonna say a clump of hair
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.29,0:16:28.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:28.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.30,0:16:33.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那孩子是不是二分裂成两个生物体了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,did that kid just separate into two organisms
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:33.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,via binary fission?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都在骑车钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been bicycle fishing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.34,注释,,0,0,0,,[ binary fission（二分裂）\N与 bicycle fishing（骑车钓鱼）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.34,0:16:36.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的挺疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:36.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It really hurts
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孩子们是不是很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aren't those kids amazing?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,迎面过来的是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what have we here?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是古怪无脑社
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the kooky Nitwitting Club
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.41,0:16:59.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋大王加入了他的无脑社社友们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:59.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Ice Cream King has joined his fellow Nitwitters
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以前从来没见过会有人那样开船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anyone drive like that before
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.63,0:17:07.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:07.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.92,0:17:10.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密配方就会归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:10.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that secret formula will be mine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:18.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(420,448)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家看到这辆花车之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, after seeing this float
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就都会冲进蟹堡王去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,everyone will rush to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.85,0:17:25.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你过期薯条准备得怎么样了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:25.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How ya set up with those expired fries, boy-o?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.31,0:17:27.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十分油滋滋  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:27.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good and greasy, boss
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready, Mr. Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.69,0:17:34.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝在我前面  害我啥都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:34.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't see a thing with SpongeBob in front of me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.82,0:17:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excellent
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.90,0:17:37.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:37.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's our turn
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.20,0:17:38.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起上场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:38.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's move it out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1080,174)}游行起点
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.87,0:17:46.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:46.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next up
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出场的是拉里健身房的健壮兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we have the Beefy Bros from Larry's Gym
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(816,200)}拉里健身房
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.13,0:17:53.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看那些头脑简单四肢发达的家伙举重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at those meatheads pump iron
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秀肌肉的样子真是令人叹为观止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's some impressive muscle hustle
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.47,0:17:58.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:58.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here comes Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她亲自当气球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As her own balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好想要那颗气球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want that balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.43,0:18:08.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星的石头是唯一不会飘的花车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:08.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's rock is one float that doesn't float
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看起来海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.19,0:18:17.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搭了美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩的无影船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:17.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has hitched a ride with Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.11,0:18:18.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:18.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,后来者不甘示弱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not to be outdone
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.37,0:18:21.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是弗雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:21.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's Fred
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.70,0:18:24.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驾着好得不得了的我的腿花车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:24.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in his incredible My Leg Mobile
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.66,0:18:25.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:25.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.95,0:18:26.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:26.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在我的腿里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in my leg
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.29,0:18:33.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我闻到了油味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:33.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I smell grease
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可不是我的味道  大王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not me you're smelling, King
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.80,0:18:38.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是蟹堡王花车的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:38.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the float from the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.93,0:18:42.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王每天把一百多万份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:42.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,serving over a million Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.05,0:18:44.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卖给了成百上千的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:44.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,daily to hundreds
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.39,0:18:47.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面的是大家最爱的小气鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:47.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's everybody's favorite tightwad
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.93,0:18:49.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:49.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.77,0:18:52.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们玩了个新花样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, there's something new--
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往场下抛薯条
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,french-fry confetti
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.37,0:19:04.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来迎接你的末日吧  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:04.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to meet your doom, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.08,0:19:11.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方在十二点钟方向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:11.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Secret formula at 12:00
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang on, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.75,0:19:16.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来有人最后一刻加入了游行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks like the parade's got a last-minute entry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这会不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:18.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd say it's some kind of
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,装了轮子的变质热狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,rancid hot dog on wheels?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.51,0:19:23.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  各位观众
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:23.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.39,0:19:24.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:24.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I believe this is
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.43,0:19:28.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村的邪恶天才  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:28.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom's own evil genius, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.35,0:19:33.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今年这么快就开始出乱子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:33.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It didn't take long for anarchy to begin this year
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯狗浪来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a rogue wave
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.86,0:19:36.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,东北风来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:36.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a nor'easter
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,暴风雨来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a perfect storm
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是一场场混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's chaos and confusion
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.82,0:19:44.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村游行的老传统了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:44.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a tradition here at the Bikini Bottom Parade
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.41,0:19:51.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来菜单上添了道新菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:51.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like there is something new on the menu
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.50,0:19:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王花车火速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab float is coming in hot
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.80,0:19:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.76,0:20:01.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿花车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:01.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My Leg Mobile
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.34,0:20:04.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们看到了一系列骨牌效应发生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:04.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here we see the domino effect in action
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My champion
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.69,0:20:14.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里我可举不了这样的重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:14.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Larry can't lift this kind of weight
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.23,0:20:20.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这场大游行迅速失控地演变成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:20.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this parade has careened into
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.24,0:20:24.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多灾多难又混乱的车祸现场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:24.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a calamitous catastrophe of crashing and chaos
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.45,0:20:29.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝贝想要拿秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:29.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Baby wants his secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.08,0:20:33.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别过来  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:33.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.83,0:20:34.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别过来  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:34.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.46,0:20:34.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:34.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.71,0:20:42.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弃花车逃命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:42.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Abandon float
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait for me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's mine
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.27,0:20:58.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:58.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's mine
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.99,0:21:04.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他为啥要抢那个没用道具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:04.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why does he want that useless prop, anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.28,0:21:09.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为海绵宝宝把秘方写到那张纸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:06.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:09.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wrote the secret formula on that paper
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.91,0:21:10.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:10.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.54,0:21:11.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:11.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.29,0:21:12.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:12.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.21,0:21:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本地加油站的最后一辆花车
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks like one last float from the local gas station
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.25,0:21:22.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以易燃物的形态加入了游行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:22.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is making a combustible entry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位观众
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well folks
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.43,0:21:30.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这场游行现已正式认定为车祸现场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:27.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this parade has now officially been
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:30.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,declared an apocalypse
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.35,0:21:36.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:36.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.19,0:21:37.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点就到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:37.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I almost had it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.44,0:21:40.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:40.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起回蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.48,0:21:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要在那罚你适当无偿加班
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where I can punish you proper with unpaid overtime
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.20,0:21:46.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你闹了这么一出傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:46.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for doing such a foolish thing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弄到了一小块
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got something--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.66,0:21:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方的其中一样原料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,an ingredient to the secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.87,0:21:56.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一样原料到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:56.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got an ingredient
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:57.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1168,796)}盐
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.46,0:21:58.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一样原料到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:58.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got an ingredient
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.00,0:22:00.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,盐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:00.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Salt
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.04,0:22:02.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:02.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.80,0:22:03.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,盐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:03.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Salt
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.05,0:22:06.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方里有盐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:06.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's got salt in it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就快破解出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm cracking the code
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.55,0:22:12.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要把盐加进正确的原料里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:12.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I have to do now is add the right ingredients to salt
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.43,0:22:13.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后快看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:13.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and voilà
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.22,0:22:16.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就有蟹黄堡秘方了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:16.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have the Krabby Patty secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.48,0:22:18.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可真是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:18.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, I really am a genius
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.48,0:22:19.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位观众
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:19.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well folks
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.48,0:22:23.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又一场裤头村游行多灾多难地结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:23.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,another Bikini Bottom Parade ends in disaster
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.36,0:22:26.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每年都一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:26.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Same as every year
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.32,0:22:27.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有啥不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:27.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.32,0:22:30.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  我想感谢我的联合主持人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.32,0:22:30.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, I'd like to thank my co-host
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.78,0:22:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋大王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Ice Cream King
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.37,0:22:33.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:33.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,King?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.62,0:22:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.62,0:22:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,King?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.41,0:22:38.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我弄到气球了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:38.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got my balloon
